                  <h2 style="font-style:underline">What Makes This Series Unique</h2>
                  <p>We aim to form lasting and meaningful relationships with our Wrolstad authors, championing their poetry careers long-term.  Unlike presses that use the guest judge/book prize format, it is our objective to continue publishing each poet we select.</p>
                  <p>Open Reading Period: October 1st - January 15th | Reading Fee: $25.00</p>
